highlights.text: Arijit Singh has the most spots on Top Songs Guwahati. Jhoome Jo Pathaan is the highest at #3.
Malang Sajna by Sachet Tandon, Parampara Tandon, and Kumaar is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Guwahati, up 56 spots at #13.
Tere Pyaar Mein by Pritam, Arijit Singh, Amitabh Bhattacharya, and Nikhita Gandhi is the highest new entry on Top Songs Guwahati at #28.
Maan Meri Jaan by King has been on Top Songs Guwahati the longest, at 13 weeks straight.
